wrapContent.value:
<cXML payloadID="${header.SAP_MessageProcessingLogID}" timestamp="${date:now:yyyy-MM-dd'T'hh:mm:ssZ}" version="1.2.060">
    <Header>
        <From>
            <Credential domain="SystemID">
                <Identity>${header.sysid}</Identity>
            </Credential>
            <Credential domain="NetworkID">
                <Identity>${header.anid}</Identity>
            </Credential>
        </From>
        <To>
            <Credential domain="VendorID">
                <Identity>${header.vendorid}</Identity>
            </Credential>
        </To>
        <Sender>
            <Credential domain="NetworkID">
                <Identity>ReplacedByGroovy</Identity>
            </Credential>
            <UserAgent>S4CORE</UserAgent>
        </Sender>
    </Header>
    <Request deploymentMode="${header.gateway}">
        <StatusUpdateRequest>
            <DocumentReference payloadID="${header.cxml_payloadID}"/>
            <Status code="200" text="Successfully Posted">"Successfully Posted"</Status>
            <IntegrationStatus documentStatus="deliverySuccessful">
                <IntegrationMessage isSuccessful="yes" type="intPackage"/>
            </IntegrationStatus>
        </StatusUpdateRequest>
    </Request>
</cXML>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE cXML SYSTEM "http://xml.cxml.org/schemas/cXML/1.2.060/cXML.dtd">
<cXML payloadID="${header.cxml_payloadID}"
      timestamp="${date:now:yyyy-MM-dd'T'hh:mm:ssZ}"
      version="1.2.060">
   <Response>
      <Status code="200" text="Success">Success</Status>
   </Response>
</cXML>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE cXML SYSTEM "http://xml.cxml.org/schemas/cXML/1.2.060/cXML.dtd">
<cXML payloadID="${header.cxml_payloadID}"
      timestamp="${date:now:yyyy-MM-dd'T'hh:mm:ssZ}"
      version="1.2.060">
   <Response>
      <Status code="200" text="Success">Success</Status>
   </Response>
</cXML>

<cXML payloadID="${header.SAP_MessageProcessingLogID}" timestamp="${date:now:yyyy-MM-dd'T'hh:mm:ssZ}" version="1.2.060">
    <Header>
        <From>
            <Credential domain="SystemID">
                <Identity>${header.sysid}</Identity>
            </Credential>
            <Credential domain="NetworkID">
                <Identity>${header.anid}</Identity>
            </Credential>
        </From>
        <To>
            <Credential domain="VendorID">
                <Identity>${header.vendorid}</Identity>
            </Credential>
        </To>
        <Sender>
            <Credential domain="NetworkID">
                <Identity>ReplacedByGroovy</Identity>
            </Credential>
            <UserAgent>S4CORE</UserAgent>
        </Sender>
    </Header>
    <Request deploymentMode="${header.gateway}">
        <StatusUpdateRequest>
            <DocumentReference payloadID="${header.cxml_payloadID}"/>
            <Status code="400" text="Failed">${exception.message}</Status>
            <IntegrationStatus documentStatus="deliveryFailed">
                <IntegrationMessage isSuccessful="no" type="intPackage"/>
            </IntegrationStatus>
        </StatusUpdateRequest>
    </Request>
</cXML>
